                            <note rend="inline" type="source">710G Peace/5: Telegram</note>
                            <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of
                                        State</gloss> to the Chairman of the American
                                    Delegation</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Hull</hi></persName>)</head>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1933-12-08T17:00:00-05:00">December 8, 1933—5
                                        p.m.</date></dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>54. Your 36, December 7, 4 p.m. Department approves proposed
                                resolution.</p>
                            <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Phillips</hi></signed></closer>
